## Segmentation Annotation

| Verb | Endpoint | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **GET** | /seg/projects | Get a list of the segmentation projects |
| **GET** | /seg/projects/:project\_name | Load a segmentation project |
| **GET** | /seg/projects/:project\_name/loadingstatus | Get the loading status of a segmentation project |
| **GET** | /seg/projects/:project\_name/filesys/:file\_sys | Initiate multiple files/folder selection |
| **GET** | /seg/projects/:project\_name/filesysstatus | Get the import status from multiple files/folder selection |
| **GET** | /seg/projects/:project\_name/uuid/:uuid/thumbnail | Get image thumbnail with metadata |
| **GET** | /seg/projects/:project\_name/uuid/:uuid/imgsrc | Get the base64 encoded image string of a data point |
| **PUT** | /seg/newproject/:project\_name | Create a new segmentation project |
| **PUT** | /seg/projects/:project\_name/uuid/:uuid/update | Update the content of a data point |
| **PUT** | /seg/projects/:project\_name/newlabels | Update the labels of a segmentation project |
| **DELETE** | /seg/projects/:project\_name | Delete a segmentation project |
| **DELETE** | /seg/projects/:project\_name/uuids | Delete a list of data points of a segmentation project |

## Bounding Box Annotation

{% api-method method="get" host="http://localhost:{port}" path="/bndbox/projects" %}
{% api-method-summary %}
Get a list of the bounding box projects
{% endapi-method-summary %}

{% api-method-description %}
Retrieve a list of project names belong to the bounding box category
{% endapi-method-description %}

{% api-method-spec %}
{% api-method-request %}

{% api-method-response %}
{% api-method-response-example httpCode=200 %}
{% api-method-response-example-description %}
**- message:** integer \(1 for success , 0 for failure\)  
**- content:** a list of string  
  
if failure occurs \(message = 0\):  
- **error\_code:** integer  
- **error\_message:** string
{% endapi-method-response-example-description %}

}
```
{% endtab %}

{% api-method method="get" host="http://localhost:{port}" path="/bndbox/projects/:project\_name/loadingstatus" %}
{% api-method-summary %}
Get the loading status of a bounding box project
{% endapi-method-summary %}

{% api-method-description %}
Check the loading status of a bounding box project.   
  
_**Note:** This endpoint should only be called after **http://localhost:{port}/bndbox/projects/:project\_name** is called earlier with the same project name._
{% endapi-method-description %}

{% api-method-spec %}
{% api-method-request %}
{% api-method-path-parameters %}
{% api-method-parameter name="project\_name" type="string" required=true %}
Project name
{% endapi-method-parameter %}
{% endapi-method-path-parameters %}
{% endapi-method-request %}

{% api-method-response %}
{% api-method-response-example httpCode=200 %}
{% api-method-response-example-description %}
**- message:** integer  
                     The category of loading status is displayed in the returning integer of **message**  
                     - **message** = 0 \(Error in loading\)  
                     - **message** = 1 \(Loading in progress\)  
                     - **message** = 2 \(Loaded successfully\)  
  
**- content:** a list contains of   
                     - **label\_list:** a list of string  
                     - **uuid\_list:** a list of integer  
  
if failure occurs \(message = 0\):  
- **error\_code:** integer  
**- error\_message:** string
{% endapi-method-response-example-description %}

{% tabs %}
{% tab title="success \(message = 1\)" %}
```
{
    "message": 1
}
```
{% endtab %}

{

        "default",
        "dog"
    ],
    "uuid_list": [
        1,

        3,
        4,
        5,
        6
    ]
}
```
{% endtab %}

{% tab title="failure \(message = 0\)" %}

{% api-method method="get" host="http://localhost:{port}" path="/bndbox/projects/:project\_name/filesysstatus" %}
{% api-method-summary %}
Get the import status from multiple files/folder selection
{% endapi-method-summary %}

{% api-method-description %}
Check the status of loading data points after selecting multiple files/folder options  
  
_**Note:** This end should only be called after **http://localhost:{port}/bndbox/projects/:project\_name/filesys/:file\_sys** is called earlier with the same project name._ 
{% endapi-method-description %}

{% api-method-spec %}
{% api-method-request %}
{% api-method-path-parameters %}
{% api-method-parameter name="project\_name" type="string" required=true %}
Project name
{% endapi-method-parameter %}
{% endapi-method-path-parameters %}
{% endapi-method-request %}

{% api-method-response %}
{% api-method-response-example httpCode=200 %}
{% api-method-response-example-description %}
**- message:** integer   
                     The category of file system status is displayed in the returning integer of **message**  
                     - **message** = 0 \(Selection window is opened\)  
                     - **message** = 1 \(Selection window is closed and no data points selected\)  
                     - **message** = 2 \(Selection window is closed and data points been uploading\)  
                     - **message** = 3 \(Selection window is closed and data points been saved to database\)  
                     - **message** = 4 \(Selection window is closed and loading completed\)  
                     - **message** = 5 \(Did not initiated\)  
  
**- uuid\_list:** a list of integer  
  
if failure occurs \(message = 5\):  
- **error\_code:** integer  
**- error\_message:** string
{% endapi-method-response-example-description %}
